# cdinsights Fields

1. heading (string)
   - The main heading for the insights section
2. tagline (string)
   - A subtitle or descriptive tagline for the insights
3. items (array of objects)
   - Repeated items listing:
     a) title (string)
     b) subtitle (string)
     c) image (image asset in Sanity)
4. selectableVariant (string)
   - "default" or "xDemo" – chosen in Sanity
5. sortOrder (number)
   - The order of this component on the page
6. globalComponentSource (reference)
   - If set, references a global cdinsights object